These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, tea
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: rose, zinnia
There are 2 different nationalities: thai, pakistani
The people have 2 different jobs:  musician, scientist
1. the musician is not to the right of the person who growszinnia##8
2. the person who growszinnia is somewhere to the left of the thai##5
3. the person drinking coffee is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |
| Beverage      | tea     | coffee      |
| Flower          | zinnia | rose    |
| Nationality         | pakistani   | thai |
| Job   | musician  | scientist      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-2::.
2 different pets are kept: lizard, horse
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: skateboarding, water-polo
The people have 2 different jobs:  librarian, software-developer
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: musical, action
1. the owner of the horse is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is somewhere to the left of the librarian##5
3. the software-developer is not to the right of the librarian##8
4. the person watching musical movies is not the person who's sport is water-polo##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |      2      |
| Pet    | lizard        | horse    |
| Sport       | skateboarding         | water-polo |
| Job         | software-developer | librarian   |
| Movie-Genre   | musical               | action  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-3::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, cain
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: folk, metal
2 different games are played: billiard, canasta
The people have 2 different jobs:  architect, pilot
1. the person playing billiard is in an odd position##4
2. the person playing canasta is not to the right of the pilot##8
3. the fan of folk is somewhere to the left of the cain-smoker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Cigar   | chaman       | cain |
| Music-Genre   | folk       | metal    |
| Game   | billiard | canasta |
| Job           | architect        | pilot   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-4::.
There 2 different types of food: cranberry, peach
2 different games are played: snooker, scrabble
City: marseilles, rome
The people use 2 different means of transport: airplane, tram
1. the person traveling to marseilles is somewhere to the right of the person playing scrabble##5
2. the person eating cranberry is not to the left of the person driving the tram##8
3. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person eating cranberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Food         | peach | cranberry  |
| Game           | scrabble  | snooker |
| City   | rome | marseilles   |
| Transport     | tram   | airplane |

