.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-5::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: documentary, scientific
The people have 2 different hobbies: singing, rock-climbing
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: classical, disco
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: zinnia, iris
1. the person who growsiris is on the far left##1
2. the fan of classical is not to the right of the person who's hobby is singing##8
3. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
4. the fan of classical is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | scientific |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing    | singing     |
| Music-Genre         | classical  | disco    |
| Flower     | iris     | zinnia       |

