2 different games are played: go, snooker
1. the fan of folk is not to the left of the person who's hobby is writing##8
2. the person playing go is the person playing go##1
3. the fan of hip-hop is somewhere to the right of the person watching fantasy movies##5
4. the person playing go is not to the right of the person playing snooker##8
5. the person playing snooker is not to the left of the fan of hip-hop##8

