.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-20::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: handball, tennis
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: september, january
There are 2 different nationalities: australian, thai
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: dubstep, classical
1. the australian is not to the right of the person who's sport is tennis##8
2. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
3. the fan of classical is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |
| Sport          | tennis         | handball    |
| Birthday           | september | january   |
| Nationality   | australian   | thai    |
| Music-Genre     | dubstep         | classical |

 